- Other section-related elements:  <body>  ,  <nav>  ,  <section>  ,  <aside>  , h1 , h2 , h3 , h4 , h5 ,
  h6 ,  <hgroup>  ,  <header>  ,  <footer>  ,  <address> 
- Using HTML sections and outlines
