<dd>: The Description Details element

Baseline Widely available

This feature is well established and works across many devices and browser versions. It’s been available
across browsers since July 2015 .

- Learn more
- <L=13#9>See full compatibility</L>
- Report feedback

The  <dd>  HTML element provides the description, definition, or value for the preceding term (  <dt>  )
in a description list (  <dl>  ).

<L=13#4>Try it</L><I=4>
<L=13#5>Attributes</L><I=5>
