  Events                         change  and  input 
  Supported common attributes    checked 
  IDL attributes                 checked  ,  indeterminate  and  value 
  DOM interface                  HTMLInputElement 
  Methods                        select() 
  Implicit ARIA Role             checkbox 
  ----------------------------- --------------------------------------------------

