  Events                                                change  and  input 

  Supported Common Attributes                           autocomplete  ,  list  ,  maxlength  ,  minlength 
                                                       ,  multiple  ,  name  ,  pattern  ,  placeholder  ,
                                                        readonly  ,  required  ,  size  , and  type 

  IDL attributes                                        list  and  value 

  DOM interface                                         HTMLInputElement 

  Methods                                               select() 

  Implicit ARIA Role                                   with no  list  attribute:  textbox 
                                                       with  list  attribute:  combobox 
  ---------------------------------------------------- ----------------------------------------------------

