<B=3g>enterkeyhint
& enterkeyhint &
            _            _              _     _       _   
  ___ _ __ | |_ ___ _ __| | _____ _   _| |__ (_)_ __ | |_ 
 / _ \ '_ \| __/ _ \ '__| |/ / _ \ | | | '_ \| | '_ \| __|
|  __/ | | | ||  __/ |  |   <  __/ |_| | | | | | | | | |_ 
 \___|_| |_|\__\___|_|  |_|\_\___|\__, |_| |_|_|_| |_|\__|
