<B=3B>translate
& translate &
 _                       _       _       
| |_ _ __ __ _ _ __  ___| | __ _| |_ ___ 
| __| '__/ _` | '_ \/ __| |/ _` | __/ _ \
| |_| | | (_| | | | \__ \ | (_| | ||  __/
